Small conversion class between HSV, HSL, and RGB

In your Makefile:
	Before your main target:
		include Color/Color.mk
	Add as a prerequisite and link with your main object somehow:
		$(COLOR_MAIN_OBJ)
	Call after pull:
		make ColorObjectDirectory
	Add as a prerequisite for clean:
		ColorClean

Four structs: (Documentation in Color.hpp)
	ColorHSL
	ColorHSV
	ColorRGB
	ColorRGBc
